6c038879-2e6a-43c5-87c4-20268d3ad05e.title: Butler
6c038879-2e6a-43c5-87c4-20268d3ad05e.text:
Good day. Would you care to hire a good butler for
5000 coins?

options.text: Tell me about your previous jobs.

22dc64da-228f-40d2-bd22-f8a648cbfd7f.title: Butler
22dc64da-228f-40d2-bd22-f8a648cbfd7f.text:
I can fulfill all [sir/madam]'s domestic service needs
with efficiency and impeccable manners. I hate to boast,
but I can say with confidence that no mortal can make
trips to the bank or sawmill faster than I!

37889248-a7e2-4094-afc0-db5aecd118d7.title: <player>
37889248-a7e2-4094-afc0-db5aecd118d7.text: Tell me about your previous jobs.

b79284ae-4883-4852-91cd-7e7326f2610d.title: Butler
b79284ae-4883-4852-91cd-7e7326f2610d.text:
From a humble beginning as a dish-washer I have worked
my way up through the ranks of domestic service in the
households of nobles from Varrock and Ardougne. As a
life-long servant I have naturally

644da217-f00e-4f66-9e4c-1d21c2bb1b05.title: Butler
644da217-f00e-4f66-9e4c-1d21c2bb1b05.text:
suppressed any personality of my own and trained myself
never to use the second person when talking to a superior.
I have usually worked in the large households of the
aristocracy, but now that such a large

01b741c4-5c20-477d-8205-2332b2dd04a4.title: Butler
01b741c4-5c20-477d-8205-2332b2dd04a4.text:
number of private persons are building their own houses
I decided to offer them my services.

dfa9946a-4712-4030-aef9-622e79989361.title: Butler
dfa9946a-4712-4030-aef9-622e79989361.text:
I must respectfully decline, sir. I offer a very
exclusive service and will only work for people with
over level 40 Construction.

2407dc84-930c-4743-807b-75ed69f84f1b.title: Butler
2407dc84-930c-4743-807b-75ed69f84f1b.text: Thank you. I can start work immediately.

args: &cYou must have a home to do that.
&cYou need a second bedroom with a bed for your servant to sleep in.
&cYou do not have enough coins to do that.
